case.name: SZAYH v Minister for Immigration & Multicultural & Indigenous Affairs [2006] FCA 240 (16 March 2006)

citances.sentence: Those orders were made against a background of extensive litigation in the Federal Magistrates Court, this Court and the High Court: see SZAYH v Minister for Immigration [2004] FMCA 771 , SZAYH v Minister for Immigration and Multicultural and Indigenous Affairs [2005] FCA 4 , SZAYH v Minister for Immigration and Multicultural and Indigenous Affairs [2005] HCATrans 353 , SZAYH v Minister for Immigration [2005] FMCA 1122 , SZAYH v Minister for Immigration and Multicultural and Indigenous Affairs [2005] FCA 1414 , SZAYH v Minister for Immigration and Multicultural and Indigenous Affairs [2006] FCA 240 , SZAYH v Minister for Immigration and Multicultural and Indigenous Affairs [2006] HCATrans 556.
